      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Meanwhile, cut the<strong> cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop the <strong>sun-dried tomatoes</strong> roughly</p>",
